<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Account Claim Approved</h1>
  
  <p>Your request to claim access to <strong><%= @provider.name %></strong> has been approved!</p>
  
  <% if @password %>
    <h2>Your Login Credentials:</h2>
    <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></p>
    <p><strong>Password:</strong> <%= @password %></p>
    <p><em>⚠️ Important: Please save these credentials securely. You can change your password after your first login.</em></p>
  <% else %>
    <p>Your existing account has been linked to this provider.</p>
    <p>If you need to reset your password, please use the "Forgot Password" feature on the login page.</p>
  <% end %>
  
  <p>
    <a href="<%= ENV.fetch('FRONTEND_URL', 'https://autismserviceslocator.com') %>/login" style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 14px 20px; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; border-radius: 4px;">
      Log In Now
    </a>
  </p>
  
  <p>You can now manage your provider profile and connect with families seeking autism services.</p>
  
  <hr>
  <p><small>This is an automated message from Autism Services Locator.</small></p>
</body>
</html>
